title: Duplicate File Detective 6.0.76 Pro (Install + Portable)
description:
*** About this release

Release date: 25/04/2016
Install: run installer, copy and replace executable from patch archive
Portable: both versions are patched, context menu not available, just unpack your version and run DFD.exe
In both cases: block internet access with your firewall, or merge reg file DisableUpdateCheck PRIOR to launching the application

*** About Duplicate File Detective 6

Find duplicate files and remove them safely, with confidence.

Duplicate File Detective uses state-of-the-art file content analysis technology to find duplicate files. You can search multiple folders, drives, removable storage devices, even network shares - all in a single pass. Then move, archive, or remove duplicates quickly and safely.

Finding and removing duplicate files does more than just free up disk space - it reduces the expense of time-consuming backup operations, brings clarity to document storage areas, speeds up file searches and indexing processes, and reduces clutter. Duplicate File Detective can even replace moved or deleted duplicate files with links to the original.

*** Features

File content analysis & optional byte-for-byte match confirmation
Find duplicates on multiple local and network paths in a single pass
Robust, built-in report scheduling with email delivery support
Clean up by moving, archiving, or removing duplicate files
Replace moved or deleted duplicate files with links to the original
User level reporting tells you who owns duplicate files

Homepage http://www.duplicatedetective.com/
